reviewText: We are enjoying these movies.  Cary Grant has a style all his own.  He is dashing - serious - loving - funny and we love it.  We can watch these films with our grandchildren and not worry about bad language or what they might see.
Grant is the original gentleman who made wonderful movies. This collection has some great ones.
I am very pleased with my purchase of the Cary Grant 7 Movie Collection.
Great titles at a very good price (I got it from either Sam's Club or BJ's for 20$). I can hardly wait for some of these to appear on BD (some already are).

It would be very good to know what movies are included.  Cary Grant made quite a few and there is no listing here to tell you what movies are included.  I even did a google search but couldn't find anything.
Nice story and I enjoyed it.
Awesomely fun collection! I enjoyed all but one of these movies!

I am happy that there is a place where I can access wonderful artwork ( movies )
which are not of the current " market ".
These treasure have as much validity now as then .... and perhaps more in that they stand on the strength of their story and not only on " flash " .
Great movie set. The price is unbeatable
